name: OOOOOOOO!!
description: OOOOOOOO!! Each cover is painted by me. There is a total of 15. It's a 12 page zine, insides are drawings by Leili Harmon and Vanessa Olivarez Comes with a hand-sculpted/ hand-painted Jack-o'-lantern! It's blind as far as what cover/pumpkin you get as once they're in the envelopes I'm grabbing them at random and sending them out. BOO!! Eat all the candy! HAPPY HALLOWEEEN!!!!
